headline: Super Micro's AI Boom Isn't Translating Into Profits (Rating Downgrade)
summary: Super Micro Computer reports 14x forward earnings, margin pressure, and competition from Dell and Nvidia through 2027. Read why SMCI stock is downgraded to hold.
